---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Sarah J Mercer
description: Build your own tools with AI. No tech background needed.
---

{% set introPost = collections.posts | first %}
{% set latestPost = collections.posts | reverse | first %}
{% set startHerePosts = [latestPost, introPost] if introPost.url != latestPost.url else [introPost] %}

<div class="hero">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">We Can Build</p>
    <h1>Build your own tools with AI.</h1>
    <p>I'm Sarah. I believe there are many smart, capable people who could be building their own software but are stuck on the launchpad. I'm on a mission to change that.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      {% if latestPost %}<a class="btn" href="{{ latestPost.url }}">Read the latest post</a>{% endif %}
      <a class="btn ghost" href="/tutorials/">See what's coming</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="portrait"><img src="/assets/images/sarah-hero.jpg" alt="Sarah J Mercer" /></div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="sec-head"><h2>Start here</h2><a href="/tutorials/">All tutorials &rarr;</a></div>
  <div class="grid">
    {% for post in startHerePosts %}
    <div class="post">
      <div class="thumb">
        {% if post.data.cover %}
          <img src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" />
        {% else %}
          [ cover image ]
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="row">
          <span class="k">{{ post.data.label or 'Tutorial' }}</span>
          {% if post.data.status %}<span class="pill live">{{ post.data.status }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
        <div class="row" style="justify-content:space-between;margin:0;">
          <span class="meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}{% if post.data.readTime %} &middot; {{ post.data.readTime }}{% endif %}</span>
          <a class="read" href="{{ post.url }}">Read &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="sec-head"><h2>Ideas I'm chewing on</h2></div>
  <p style="color:#54585f;font-size:16px;margin:0 0 18px;max-width:640px;">Lesson 1 is up. Here's the rough shape of what might come next. The order will shift, some of these might turn into something else, and a few new ones will probably appear.</p>
  <div class="grid3">
    <div class="card idea"><p class="k">Next up</p><h4>A small everyday tool</h4><p>A decision log, a converter, a "what should I cook" picker &mdash; same shape as the habit tracker, different use.</p></div>
    <div class="card idea"><p class="k">A bit later</p><h4>Tools that remember things</h4><p>The step from one-shot HTML to "my tool remembers what I told it last time".</p></div>
    <div class="card idea"><p class="k">The big one, maybe</p><h4>A passive time recorder</h4><p>The tool that started all of this for me. Still the destination.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="sec-head"><h2>Just want to use the tools?</h2></div>
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="ph"><img src="/assets/images/nimble-tech-logo.svg" alt="Nimble Tech" /></div>
    <div>
      <span class="tag">Nimble Tech</span>
      <h3>Don't want to build things yourself? Check out Nimble Tech's library of tools.</h3>
      <p>I run Nimble Tech alongside this. It's where the tools I've finished and polished actually live, ready to use straight away. Built mostly for lawyers and the firms they work in, all aimed at taking the dull bits off your plate.</p>
      <a class="btn" href="https://nimbletech.uk">Visit Nimble Tech &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="band" id="signup">
  <h3>Want each tutorial in your inbox?</h3>
  <p>One short email when a new build-along goes live. No spam, no jargon.</p>
  <form class="form" action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/WeCanBuild" method="post">
    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="you@email.com" aria-label="Email address" required />
    <button class="btn" type="submit">Subscribe</button>
  </form>
  <p class="bd-credit"><a href="https://buttondown.com/refer/WeCanBuild" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Powered by Buttondown</a></p>
</div>
